Migration.Name: Create process to transfer funds between BPartners

PO.Data: This process provides a quick means of transferring funds from one Business Partner Account to another using an invoice and credit memo. Both Business Partners have to be customers and the source or From account has to have a credit balance. After the transfer is made, the invoice and credit memo can be allocated using the Payment Allocation window.
Transfer funds between Business Partners in one operation by creating an invoice and credit memo.
